---
title: Balsamic Steak with Red cabbage and Potato Wedges
description: In Mimi’s house, steak reigns supreme. Along with chocolate and horse racing, it’s something the whole family can agree on. They all love their steak super-rare; what the French would call ‘bleu’. So much so that Mimi’s mum doesn’t even know how to cook a steak well done! But don’t worry, however you like your steak cooked, this recipe will taste sensational.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/balsamic-steak-wk-19-0241ead1-bedc9008.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.co.uk/recipecards/card/balsamic-steak-wk-19-58ca637a2310a860a428bb73-219eab68.pdf
author: Mimi Morley
cuisine: British
course: main course
time required: 40 minutes
servings: 2
source: https://www.hellofresh.co.uk/recipes/balsamic-steak-wk-19-58ca637a2310a860a428bb73
nutrition:
  calories: 475 kcal
